me":"2019-08-20T02:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2407f3aa724b83df9e2830a70c04d44af0b35553","tid":1488903,"uid":146583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:00:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3e89d16b79dfae0738a7362488786d885afb8cd","tid":1488903,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98vewC3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98vewC3.jpg&h=1f78dabd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vvxMnKL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvvxMnKL.jpg&h=8f43322b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RygEHKT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRygEHKT.jpg&h=55a9da1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qhgtA4V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqhgtA4V.jpg&h=f5f34c2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7853afbcc2ebd94cf45921c33409d5431884abfd","tid":1488903,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:19:08.000Z","msg":"屬於香港既#metoo行動上線啦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1490165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1490165</a><br />\n<br />\n國際關注！國際關注！"},{"pid":"f43f46394af6241b87e1cfae17b328bc4ba291c2","tid":1488903,"uid":296193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:52:00.000Z","msg":"821元朗事件一個月靜坐活動：<br />\nDress code: 黑衫，口罩<br />\n個人護身（optional）<br />\nLv 1 行山杖，電筒，鐳射槍<br />\nLv 2 安全帽，眼罩，豬嘴（未必用得著）<br />\nLv 3 自己improve, 到時人多，地方窄，太重裝反而容易令人不安<br />\n<br />\n文宣：印多d出來，手持，派比乘客，貼文，貼到元西變連儂站。<br />\n<br />\n垃圾：回收多餘用不着的文宣，保持地方整潔<br />\n<br />\n玩乜：靜坐/默站/叫口號，自發留空間比街坊居民返屋企同搭車走，後join的手足向Yoho方向聚集。<br />\n<br />\n西鐵唔停嘅話點算：朗屏站行過元朗站好快，再唔係天水圍站轉輕鐵。<br />\n<br />\n附近景點：元朗站下面有連儂牆。Yoho商場24小時通道。如有手足賴嘢，隔離就係博愛醫院.....<br />\n<br />\n禁止進入地方：雞地（鳳琴街一帶）唔好去，除非識路，圍村唔好入。<br />\n<br />\n安全事項：唔好落單，同朋友一齊行動。照顧街坊，照顧細路及老人家。唔好主動同人郁手，但有心理準備有人挑戰，元朗係重深藍黑區域。小心鬼，小心黑社會，小心痴線佬。<br />\n<br />\n遇到人搞事：以「自衛」及「制服」為目的處理，唔好亂捉鬼捉錯自己人，因為而家鬼會主動撩人捉鬼，所以手足即使勇武都唔好開口埋口吊老帽嚇親自己人。<br />\n<br />\n完左點走：應該好多手足住屯元天識路，可經Yoho天橋去大馬路專輕鐵。外面的手足，出市區西鐵應該會運作正常，冇嘅話Yoho 天橋對面有巴士走，或者經Yoho去返大馬路有巴士小巴出市區。<br />\n<br />\n有冇下場：唔知，自己決定，Be Water.<br />\n不割席。不分化。不篤灰。"},{"pid":"d1d4943783f12ec406bfa8e6a110c6b7ffcc46c0","tid":1488903,"uid":81008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:18:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5adc67bc6a8fbd0607b6775521565472b53a8e4","tid":1488903,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:25:12.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"b79e80696c739c65aa64924d073cdd168303259a","tid":1488903,"uid":13119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:33:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb748d9c3d838b94cf13e03523a17057bb51f458","tid":1488903,"uid":196538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab11e9bd426c1ade7b79aa78db7bb786769a70f7","tid":1488903,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:32:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5a971c84072913414ee983afb2ef714ba1d6bf61","tid":1488903,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:32:49.000Z","msg":"收工即到 已準備好奮死保護各位安全"},{"pid":"8e46c293db94374f86bb10d43da4b5d49c3c31ef","tid":1488903,"uid":252292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:33:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bdaa814cb50c12780cbd2d1f98f6ee3b740828bc","tid":1488903,"uid":182998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:39:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"508933d21b8871616a8fbc33f0e6ad18fefcf43d","tid":1488903,"uid":65089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:41:15.000Z","msg":"821 靜坐"},{"pid":"6e3